fields.name: Anthelios Ultralight Invisible Fluid SPF50+ Suncream 50ml
fields.description:
Keep skin nourished and protected with the La Roche-Posay Anthelios Ultra-Light Invisible Fluid SPF50+ Sun Cream. The lightweight, fluid glides effortlessly across skin, absorbing fast leaving skin feeling fresh. Developed specifically for sensitive skin, the extremely high-protection sun cream creates a powerful barrier against the harsh rays of the sun, reducing the risk of burning and irritation.

The sun cream goes above and beyond with a PPD (Persistent Pigment Darkening) Factor of 46, which is stricter than the European recommendation for sun protection. This is due to an ingenious and patented technology known as Mexoplex®, allowing the sun screen to offer optimum protection against harsh external aggressors. An infusion of gentle La Roche-Posay Thermal Spring Water hydrates the skin, working to replenish as it shields.

The formula boasts impressive stay power, with sand, sweat and water-resistant features allowing you total peace of mind that you will not have to excessively re-apply the product. White marks and stains will become a thing of the past, while the UVA, UVB and Infrared protection shields delicate and damage-prone skin in a veil of defence. Complete with a minimalist formula, you can be safe in the knowledge that no nasty or unnecessary chemicals are coming into contact with your skin.

fields.name: Lait-Crème Concentré Multi-Purpose Moisturiser 75ml
fields.description:
Embryolisse Lait-Crème Concentré is a three-in-one moisturising lotion, primer and make-up remover. Its rich formula contains essential fatty acids and vitamins to reduce irritation especially after shaving and plump skin for firmer results.

Enriched with nutrients and water to balance skin and promote cell renewal to leave skin supple and healthy-looking. The lotion delivers a satin film to reduce dryness discomfort for a soft, radiant complexion and is suitable for use as a repairing mask, to cleanse skin, or as a baby-care product.

fields.name: C E Ferulic Antioxidant Vitamic C Serum 30ml
fields.description:
Attaining cult status amongst skincare enthusiasts, SkinCeuticals C E Ferulic Serum is designed to offer advanced protection against environmental aggressors. Combining a trio of hero ingredients, the daytime vitamin C serum promotes a radiant complexion, while helping to soften the appearance of fine lines.

A synergistic antioxidant blend of vitamins C, E and ferulic acid, helps to improve the visible signs of photo-damage, promoting a brighter and more evenly-toned visage. Supporting a radiant and smooth-looking complexion, the serum provides the ideal addition to your environmental defence skincare regime.

fields.name: Lip Conditioner 4g
fields.description: Formulated with 99% naturally-derived ingredients, Caudalie Lip Conditioner is a beauty treatment for the lips that repairs damaged lips with each application. With anti-oxidant properties, it also delivers nutrition and protection for the lips all day long.

fields.name: Effaclar Duo+ Unifant Medium 40ml
fields.description:
Perfect your skin in a single step with the multi-tasking Effaclar Duo+ Unifiant Moisturiser in the shade 'Medium' from La Roche-Posay. The lightweight moisturiser contains all of the award-winning benefits of the best-selling Effaclar blemish treatment, with the addition of a subtle tint to create a natural, even complexion.

It provides sheer coverage that visibly reduces the appearance of redness and imperfections, and with continued use skin’s texture appears more refined and mattified. Key ingredients include Niacinamide to purify, LHA Solution to exfoliate and Salicylic Acid to help repair damaged cells. Recommended for oily, blemish-prone skin, the transformative solution penetrates clogged pores to clear blackheads and other impurities. Expect clear, healthier-looking and radiant skin.

Non-comedogenic. Free from parabens.

fields.name: Boy Brow
fields.description: A brushable, creamy wax that visibly thickens, shapes, and grooms brows into place. Inspired by traditional hair pomade, it gives brows soft, flexible hold in one easy swipe, and doesn't stiffen or flake. Contains Oleic Acid, Lecithin, and Soluble Collagen to condition and moisturize brows.

fields.name: Lash Stick
fields.description:
Bestselling mascara that visibly lengthens and lifts lashes (without smudges or flakes) for a baby extensions effect. Lash Slick’s weightless, flexible formula enhances the look of your natural lashes. The secret’s in teeny-tiny fibers that coat each individual hair from root to tip creating maximum definition and length—think less “your mascara looks good” and more “your lashes look good”.

It’s water-resistant, not waterproof—that means it stays in place without smudging or flaking for up to 12 hours, but then removes easily with warm water (and without harsh, damaging rubbing) when you’re ready to take it off. As your everyday mascara, nourishing ingredients like Pro-Vitamin B5 and Biotinyl Tripeptide-1 help support sleek, shiny, cared-for lashes long term

fields.name: Gloss Bomb - Sweet Mouth
fields.description:
One luscious swipe of Gloss Bomb’s XXL wand gives lips more to love, while conditioning Shea butter enriches from within. Lips look instantly fuller and smoother, with a non-sticky formula that’s super shiny and has an addictive peach-vanilla scent you just can’t get enough of.

Fenty Beauty was created with a vision. For creator and founder Rihanna, it was essential “that women everywhere would be included”. After recognising a void in the industry, Rihanna focused on a range of traditionally hard to match skin tones, developing formulas that work for all skin types, and pinpointing universal shades. Her aim, above all, is to inspire: “Makeup is there for you to have fun with. It should never feel like pressure. It should never feel like a uniform. Feel free to take chances, and take risks, and dare to do something new or different.”

fields.name: Volume 9 Issue 2
fields.description: A thing of beauty and permanence in an age of transience. Since 1998.

fields.name: Loving Candle
fields.description:
“Loving is the private doodle as you think of your Amour. The chain stitch represents the labour of love involved in creating this first memento - which may never actually be sent. The pleasure is in the fantasy” - Bella Freud.

Handpicked ingredients add a magnetic seductive touch to this formulation with tantalising notes of Tuberose Absolute sitting in the heart, caressed by the warmth of Amber Crystals silently balanced by Sandalwood.

fields.name: Gel Ink Ballpoint Pen 0.5mm
fields.description:
Cap-type ballpoint pen in an original design 

Supplied with refill for Gel Ink Pens

fields.name: Colbalt Teapot
fields.description:
Expertly handcrafted in Devon from fine bone china, each piece in the elegant Cobalt China Collection is finished with a transparent glaze that brings out the crisp white finish of the china and enhances its dimpled profile. Beautifully minimalist, each piece is completed by a deep-cobalt hand-painted accent.

Committed to crafting designs with lifelong durability, Feldspar designs each piece from its thatched studio overlooking Dartmoor. Supporting local business, its designs are crafted by skilled craftspeople across the UK using the finest local materials.
